Digital Equipment Corp andSystems Industries Inc &lt;SYSM> said they settled all pendinglitigation between the two companies.    They said Digital's 1980 patent infringement suit againstSystems Industries was dismissed, as was Systems Industries'1986 antitrust suit against Digital.    The companies said Systems Industries will be licensed tomanufacture computer mass storage devices that use Digitaltechnology.    They also said the company will pay Digital royalties insettlement of Digital's patent infringement claims. Reuter&#3;